<td style=" color:#000000; font-size:12pt; background-color:#FFFFFF; font-family:arial; bLabel:main; bEditID:r3st1;" tEditID="c1r1" locked="0" aEditID="c1r1" >
<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.FirstName},</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><b style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="line-height: 18px;"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></span></b></div><div style="text-align: center;"><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">You recently completed the Essential Information Form which communicates to us information necessary to both complete your pre employment screening and to set up your payroll records. &nbsp;Unfortunately, part of the form malfunctioned and did not allow you to make a full tax declaration which is vital in order for us to establish which tax code you should be working on.</font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">&nbsp;</font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Please therefore indicate which of the following three statements is relevant to you and will reflect your circumstances at the point at which you commence work with TCN this summer:</font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">&nbsp;</font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">A – This is my first job since last 6 April and&nbsp;</font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">I have not been receiving taxable Jobseeker's</span></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Allowance, Employment and Support Allowance&nbsp;</font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">or taxable Incapacity Benefit or a state or</span></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">occupational pension.</font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">&nbsp;</font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">OR</font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">B – This is now my only job, but since last 6 April&nbsp;</font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">I have had another job, or have received</span></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">taxable Jobseeker's Allowance,&nbsp;</font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">Employment and Support Allowance or&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">taxable Incapacity Benefit. I do not receive&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">a state or occupational pension.</span></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">&nbsp;</font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">OR</font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">C – I have another job or receive a state or&nbsp;</font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;">occupational pension.&nbsp;</span></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Please respond as soon as possible to crb@the-challenge.org</font></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Yours sincerely,</font></div><div style="text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Lucy Found</font></div><div style="text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">crb@the-challenge.org</font></div><div style="text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Evolution Recruitment, on behalf of</font></div><div style="text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">The Challenge Network</font></div>]]></td>
